with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as dirname:
    make_website_files(profile, dirname)
    for filename in os.listdir(pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__,
        f'{WEBSITE_DIR}/{files_dir}')):
        assert filecmp.cmp(os.path.join(dirname, WEBSITE_DIR, filename),
            pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__,
            f'{WEBSITE_DIR}/{files_dir}/{filename}'), shallow=False) is True
